(2365, 2, '2016-10-08 11:42:46', '2016-10-08 11:42:46', '[vc_row css_animation=\"fadeIn\" css=\".vc_custom_1555586760942{padding-top: 0px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;background-color: #ffffff !important;}\"][vc_column css=\".vc_custom_1475853057895{padding: 0px !important;}\"][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1555586680645{padding-top: 0px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1555237469839{padding-top: 25px !important;padding-right: 15px !important;padding-bottom: 25px !important;padding-left: 15px !important;background-color: #ffffff !important;}\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<div class=\"career_box\">\r\n<div class=\"career_box_heading\">\r\n<h1>Designer</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n<h4>Graphics Designer</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>At Zitrone Solutions we need a Experienced Candidate for Graphics Designing at Surat. We need a designer who is creative in designing.</li>\r\n 	<li>Company works with Mobile app development only.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Experience, Skills and Responsibilities :</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Experience in Web and Mobile Application UI design, E mailer, Newsletters, PPT Presentation.</li>\r\n 	<li>Knowledge of HTML5, CSS3 to understand how things getting done in web browser.</li>\r\n 	<li>Expertise in Photoshop, Illustrator, Dreamweaver, In design, Firework and Prototyping tools.</li>\r\n 	<li>The designer will also be expected to design the overall functionality of the product, and in order to ensure a great user experience, iterate upon it in accordance with user-testing.</li>\r\n 	<li>Experience working with Photoshop, Illustrator, Graphic Designing, User Interface Designing, Dreamweaver, HTML5, CSS3.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Benefits</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Increment will be given after one year of job completed.</li>\r\n 	<li>Company provide 12 paid leaves per year.</li>\r\n 