 in Core PHP, MySQL, WordPress Framework.</li>\r\n 	<li>Having Experience working with Codeignitor is an aided benifit.</li>\r\n 	<li>Having Knowledge of RESTful API Development and Implementation.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Benefits</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Increment will be given after one year of job completed.</li>\r\n 	<li>Company provide 12 paid leaves per year.</li>\r\n 	<li>Working days  Monday to Saturday</li>\r\n 	<li>Working Hours - 9:00 - 6:00</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"line\"><strong>Job Type : </strong>Full Time\r\n<strong>Salary : </strong>12,000.00 to 15,000.00 /month\r\n<strong>Experience : </strong>Web Development 1 year (Preferred)\r\n<strong>Education : </strong>Bachelor\'s (Preferred)\r\n<strong>Location: </strong> Surat, Gujarat</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"send_cv_block\">You can send your CV here : <a href=\"mailto:career@zitronesolutions.com\"><strong>career@zitronesolutions.com</strong></a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1555237493862{padding-top: 25px !important;padding-right: 15px !important;padding-bottom: 25px !important;padding-left: 15px !important;background-color: #ffffff !important;}\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<div class=\"career_box\">\r\n<div class=\"career_box_heading\">\r\n<h1>Android</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n<h4>Android Developer</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>At Zitrone Solutions we need a Experienced Candidate for Android Development at Surat. We need a developer who can Work in team.</li>\r\n 	<li>Company works with Mobile app development only.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Responsibilities and Duties :</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Collaborate with Team leader, designer and testers to analyze, define and execute the development process.</li>\r\n 	<li>Clearly understand requirement and suggest their own idea to make better features in app development.</li>\r\n 	<li>Continuously discover, evaluate, and implement new technologies to maximize development efficiency.</li>\r\n 	<li>Develop advanced applications for the Android platform.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Required Experience, Skills and Qualifications :</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Education Qualification: MSCIT, MCA, IT Engg, Computer Engg.</li>\r\n 	<li>Experience Qualification: Up to 1-year job experience in android, worked on android studio</li>\r\n 	<li>Having good understanding App development cycle and Android SDK.</li>\r\n 	<li>Use of open source library with gradle systems.</li>\r\n 	<li>Understand Android UI/UX design Principles and Patterns.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Benefits</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Increment will be given after one year of job completed.</li>\r\n 	<li>Company provide 12 paid leaves per year.</li>\r\n 	<li>Working days  Monday to Saturday</li>\r\n 	<li>Working Hours - 9:00 - 6:00</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"line\"><strong>Job Type : </strong>Full Time\r\n<strong>Salary : </strong>13,000.00 to 20,000.00 /month\r\n<strong>Experience : </strong>Android Development 1 year (Preferred)\r\n<strong>Education : </strong>Bachelor\'s (Preferred)\r\n<strong>Agile Experience Needed </strong>\r\n<strong>Location: </strong> Surat, Gujarat</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"send_cv_block\">You can send your CV here : <a href=\"mailto:career@zitronesolutions.com\"><strong>career@zitronesolutions.com</strong></a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Career at Zitrone Solutions', '\n						', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'career', '', '', '2020-12-21 11:05:40', '2020-12-21 11:05:40', '', 361, 'http://keydesign-themes.com/incubator/corporate/?page_id=2365', 51, 'page', '', 0),
